 services,
 and infrastructure operated or managed by the Information Operations Department.
 Governed activities include:
 Business Impact Analysis (BIA) development and maintenance,
 asset criticality classification,
 Recovery Time Objective (RTO) and Recovery Point Objective (RPO) definition,
 Continuity Plan development and maintenance,
 backup governance framework requirements,
 continuity plan activation,
 and operational recovery sequencing following plan activation or Operational Handback from Chapter 4.The following are outside the scope of this policy:
